# n8n-cold-email-ai-tracking

Automated cold email outreach system built with **n8n**, using **Google Sheets** as the source, **Gmail** for sending and receiving emails, and **OpenAI** to analyze customer interest and trigger intelligent follow-up replies.

---

## ğŸš€ Overview

This automation monitors new rows added to a Google Sheet, sends cold emails automatically, tracks replies in Gmail, and uses AI to determine customer interest. Based on the analysis, it can send appropriate follow-up responses without manual intervention.

---

## ğŸ§© Workflows Included

### 1. SS01 â€“ Cold Email Tracking Automation
- Triggers when a new row is added to Google Sheets
- Sends a cold email via Gmail
- Logs email activity for tracking

### 2. SS01 â€“ Check Customer Interest & Send Reply
- Monitors Gmail inbox for replies
- Uses OpenAI to analyze customer intent
- Automatically sends follow-up responses based on interest level

