---

## ğŸ”„ How It Works (Flow Summary)

1. New row added to Google Sheet
2. n8n detects the new entry
3. Cold email is sent via Gmail
4. Gmail inbox is monitored for replies
5. OpenAI analyzes the reply content
6. System determines customer interest
7. Automated follow-up email is sent (if applicable)

---

## âš™ï¸ Setup Notes

- Update Google Sheets credentials in n8n
- Connect Gmail account with proper permissions
- Add your OpenAI API key in n8n credentials
- Review prompt logic inside OpenAI nodes for customization

